## Offline-First Pattern

All reads: expo-sqlite first → render → then sync Supabase in background
All writes: write to expo-sqlite immediately → optimistic UI → sync to Supabase
On reconnect: pull diffs, resolve conflicts (last-write-wins for personal use)

This ensures the app works fully during poor connectivity (Tier 2/3 use case).

