## Environment Variables Required

```
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=          # server-side only (edge functions), never in app bundle
OPENAI_API_KEY=             # server-side only (Whisper), never in app bundle
```

API keys for Claude and Whisper must ONLY exist in Supabase Edge Function secrets.
Never put them in the Expo app bundle. Use EXPO_PUBLIC_ prefix only for public keys.
